kesako.common

Class ResultDoc

  • java.lang.Object
    • kesako.common.ResultDoc

  • public class ResultDoc
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a result item from a research. It is composed by the data necessary to display a result
    The class implements the Log4J logging system.
    Author:
    Frederic SACHOT
